trans-unit.source: Provides a base class for design-time support for controls that derive from <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataBoundControl"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Inneholder en basisklasse for utforming støtte for kontroller som er avledet fra <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataBoundControl"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Extend the DataBoundControlDesigner class if you want to create a designer for the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataBoundControl> Web server control or for a class that extends <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataBoundControl>.
trans-unit.target: Utvide klassen DataBoundControlDesigner Hvis du vil opprette en utformer for <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataBoundControl>Web serverkontroll eller for en klasse som utvider <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataBoundControl>.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataBoundControl> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataBoundControl>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.DataBoundControlDesigner"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.DataBoundControlDesigner"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: Gets the <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionListCollection"></xref> object for this designer.
trans-unit.target: Henter den <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionListCollection"> </xref> objekt for utformeren.

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionListCollection"></xref> object associated with this designer.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionListCollection"> </xref> tilknyttet utformeren.

trans-unit.source: Disconnects events from the previous data source and connects them to the current data source.
trans-unit.target: Kobler hendelser fra forrige datakilden, og kobles til den gjeldende datakilden.

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if the data-bound control connected to a new data source; <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref> if the data source did not change.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Hvis databundet kontrollen som er koblet til en ny datakilde; <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref> om datakilden ikke endret.

trans-unit.source: Invokes the standard dialog box to create a new data source control, and sets the new data source control's ID to the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.BaseDataBoundControl.DataSourceID*> property of the data-bound control.
trans-unit.target: Aktiverer standard dialogboksen for å opprette en ny datakildekontroll, og angir nye datakilde kontrollens IDen til den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.BaseDataBoundControl.DataSourceID*>egenskapen kontrollens databundet.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.BaseDataBoundControl.DataSourceID*>

trans-unit.source: Binds the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataBoundControl"></xref> object to the data source.
trans-unit.target: Binding av <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataBoundControl"> </xref> objektet til datakilden.

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataBoundControl"></xref> object to bind to the data source.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataBoundControl"> </xref> objektet skal bindes til datakilden.

trans-unit.source: Gets the shadowed <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataBoundControl.DataMember*> property of the underlying data-bound control.
trans-unit.target: Henter den skyggelagt <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataBoundControl.DataMember*>egenskapen kontrollens underliggende databindingselementer.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataBoundControl.DataMember*>

trans-unit.source: The shadowed <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataBoundControl.DataMember*> of the underlying data-bound control.
trans-unit.target: Den skyggelagt <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataBoundControl.DataMember*>kontrollens underliggende databindingselementer.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataBoundControl.DataMember*>

trans-unit.source: Gets the designer of the data source of the underlying data-bound control.
trans-unit.target: Henter utformeren av datakilden kontrollens underliggende databundet.

trans-unit.source: The designer of the data source of the underlying data-bound control.
trans-unit.target: Utformeren av datakilden kontrollens underliggende databundet.

trans-unit.source: Gets the <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerDataSourceView"></xref> object associated with the data source of this designer.
trans-unit.target: Henter den <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerDataSourceView"> </xref> tilknyttet datakilden utformeren.

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerDataSourceView"></xref> object associated with the data source of this designer.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerDataSourceView"> </xref> tilknyttet datakilden utformeren.

trans-unit.source: Disconnects the data-bound control from data source events.
trans-unit.target: Kobler databundet-kontrollen fra datakildehendelser.

trans-unit.source: Releases the unmanaged resources used by the <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.DataBoundControlDesigner"></xref> object and optionally releases the managed resources.
trans-unit.target: Frigir uforvaltede ressursene som brukes av den <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.DataBoundControlDesigner"> </xref> objekt og eventuelt frigir administrerte ressurser.

trans-unit.source: The Dispose method unregisters the designer's event handlers from all data source events.
trans-unit.target: Fjerningsmetoden Avregistrerer den utformeren hendelsesbehandling fra alle datakildehendelser.

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> to release both managed and unmanaged resources; <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref> to release only unmanaged resources.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Frigi ressurser både administrerte og uforvaltede; <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref> frigi bare uforvaltede ressurser.

trans-unit.source: Gets the design-time data source from either the associated <xref uid="langword_csharp_DataSourceDesigner" name="DataSourceDesigner" href=""></xref> or the <xref uid="langword_csharp_DataSource" name="DataSource" href=""></xref> property.
trans-unit.target: Henter datakilden utformingen fra enten den tilknyttede <xref uid="langword_csharp_DataSourceDesigner" name="DataSourceDesigner" href=""> </xref> eller <xref uid="langword_csharp_DataSource" name="DataSource" href=""> </xref> egenskapen.

trans-unit.source: An object that implements an <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerable> interface referencing the design-time data source.
trans-unit.target: Et objekt som implementerer en <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerable>grensesnittet refererer til datakilden utformingen.</xref:System.Collections.IEnumerable>

trans-unit.source: Gets dummy sample data to render the data-bound control on the design surface if sample data cannot be created from the <xref uid="langword_csharp_DataSourceDesigner" name="DataSourceDesigner" href=""></xref> or <xref uid="langword_csharp_DataSource" name="DataSource" href=""></xref> properties.
trans-unit.target: Henter midlertidige eksempeldata å gjengi databundet kontrollen i utformingsoverflaten Hvis eksempeldata ikke kan opprettes fra den <xref uid="langword_csharp_DataSourceDesigner" name="DataSourceDesigner" href=""> </xref> eller <xref uid="langword_csharp_DataSource" name="DataSource" href=""> </xref> egenskaper.

trans-unit.source: An object that implements the <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerable> interface containing dummy sample data used to render the data-bound control on the design surface.
trans-unit.target: Et objekt som implementerer den <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerable>grensesnittet med midlertidige eksempeldata brukes til å gjengi databundet kontrollen i utformingsoverflaten.</xref:System.Collections.IEnumerable>

trans-unit.source: Overridden by the designer to shadow run-time properties of the data-bound control with corresponding properties implemented by the designer.
trans-unit.target: Overstyres av designer til skyggen kjøretid egenskaper kontrollens databundet tilsvarende egenskapene implementeres av utformeren.

trans-unit.source: Override the PreFilterProperties method to perform any additional actions required when the data source of the underlying data-bound control changes.
trans-unit.target: Overstyr PreFilterProperties-metoden for å utføre noen flere handlinger kreves når datakilden kontrollens underliggende databundet endres.

trans-unit.source: An <xref:System.Collections.IDictionary> object containing the properties to filter.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.Collections.IDictionary>objektet som inneholder egenskapene til å filtrere.</xref:System.Collections.IDictionary>

trans-unit.source: Gets the number of rows that the data-bound control displays on the design surface.
trans-unit.target: Henter antall rader som databundet kontrollen skal vises på utformingsoverflaten.
